{"tid":2264734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳姑娘︰(專家食屎)支那疫情非常穩定　豁免安排無問題","createTime":"2020-10-31T01:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T05:21:59.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"24f98a84b2501457f231bdf4b068908e499ad8bb","tid":2264734,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T01:47:09.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>第三波血的教訓？我他媽的唔在乎，奶共是真理！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557631-20201031.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557631-20201031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=42977e3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557631-20201031.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a8d99c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557631-20201031.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n一名昨日確診、感染源頭未明的44歲男子，曾在9月底至10月初到訪深圳，從深圳返港後獲豁免檢疫。食物及衞生局長陳肇始說，患者在潛伏期之外的時間往返內地，當局仍在追蹤他的活動情況和感染源頭。陳肇始又說，內地目前疫情非常穩定，認為本港的豁免安排並無問題，不會因為今次個案卻步。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始出席一個電台節目時又說，目前有不少港人在大灣區城市居住，居於內地的港人回港後豁免14天強制檢疫安排，將於下月之內展開，初時會設有配額。至於食衞局與創科局聯手的「健康碼」研發工作已經完成，但香港與內地通關的先決條件，是本港疫情要得到控制，政制及內地事務局正與內地當局商討有關安排。"},{"pid":"0254ab57b3311e84232903dd8c5ca1792f9a9d14","tid":2264734,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T01:50:15.000Z","msg":"支那臭屎密冚緊係穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7e259dd8f7ce650b428f03e14cad59a3d3b7de","tid":2264734,"uid":27605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"穩定=增加減少數量唔多 但本身已經好多"},{"pid":"73bc91897d726dc3ba10220ec7f7fa8406f33851","tid":2264734,"uid":208511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T01:50:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large